  "title": "ng.getDirectives",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/global\", \"name\": \"@angular/core/global\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\", \"name\": \"ng.getDirectives\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a> > <a href=\"api/core/global\">@angular/core/global</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L231-L295\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts#L231-L295\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"nggetdirectives\">ng.getDirectives<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives#nggetdirectives\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label global\">global</label>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Retrieves directive instances associated with a given DOM node. Does not include\ncomponent instances.</p>\n<p>检索与给定 DOM 元素关联的指令实例。不包括组件实例。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\">ng.getDirectives</span>(node: Node): {}[]</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>node</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>Node</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>DOM node for which to get the directives.</p>\n<p>要为其获取指令的 DOM 元素。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code>{}[]</code>: Array of directives associated with the node.</p>\n<p>与元素关联的指令数组。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Given the following DOM structure:</p>\n<p>给定以下 DOM 结构：</p>\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&#x3C;app-root>\n  &#x3C;button my-button>&#x3C;/button>\n  &#x3C;my-comp>&#x3C;/my-comp>\n&#x3C;/app-root>\n</code-example>\n<p>Calling <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\" class=\"code-anchor\">getDirectives</a></code> on <code>&#x3C;button></code> will return an array with an instance of the <code>MyButton</code>\ndirective that is associated with the DOM node.</p>\n<p>在 <code>&#x3C;button></code> 上调用 <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\" class=\"code-anchor\">getDirectives</a></code> 将返回一个数组，该数组带有与 DOM 元素关联 <code>MyButton</code></p>\n<p>Calling <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\" class=\"code-anchor\">getDirectives</a></code> on <code>&#x3C;my-comp></code> will return an empty array.</p>\n<p>在 <code>&#x3C;my-comp></code> 上调用 <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetDirectives\" class=\"code-anchor\">getDirectives</a></code> 将返回一个空数组。</p>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/global\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/global\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectives#nggetdirectives\n - api/core/global/ngGetDirectives#usage-notes\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L231-L295\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/15.0.1/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts#L231-L295\n-->"
}